            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-39aa2e6a-9067-4326-a900-9f0346a66945">
                Mr. Henderson Stewart  (Fife, East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-39aa2e6a-9067-4326-a900-9f0346a66945" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
