</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-a3f7d32f-1833-4e93-b0b8-9ee9c98793f0">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-a3f7d32f-1833-4e93-b0b8-9ee9c98793f0">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
