            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cfcdf25c-4330-4a3e-b88d-853554177a7a">
                Mr. Woodburn (Clackmannan and East Stirlingshire)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cfcdf25c-4330-4a3e-b88d-853554177a7a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-20/debates/e5750671-c9de-43bb-94c8-313978d990ec/OverseasResourcesDevelopmentBill#contribution-cfcdf25c-4330-4a3e-b88d-853554177a7a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
