    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The only point I am making is that the hon. Gentleman did not at the time so advise his own party, who approved this Scheme.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-84596659-fe8a-4e84-b9b6-b78c5c36b473" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-20/debates/e5750671-c9de-43bb-94c8-313978d990ec/OverseasResourcesDevelopmentBill#contribution-84596659-fe8a-4e84-b9b6-b78c5c36b473">
