<p class=""><em>indicated dissent.</em></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d24a9dc6-e548-4157-be03-ecdfc4ce3cd3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
