<p class="">Thirty-six and a half million.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-62af5de9-ca7e-4f39-9039-a38043f41dd1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
