on, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, J Baker (Canterbury)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Howard, Gerald (Cambridgeshire)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Orr-Ewing, Ian L. (Weston-super-Mare)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Williams, C. (Torquay)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, Sir Austin (Lewisham, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Osborne, C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Williams, Gerald (Tonbridge)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, Rt. Hon. R. S. (Southport)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peake, Rt. Hon. O</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Williams, Sir H. G. (Croydon, E)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hudson, W. R. A. (Hull, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Perkins, W. R. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wills, G.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hulbert, Wing-Cdr. N. J</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peto, Brig. C. H. M</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wilson, Geoffrey (Truro)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hurd, A. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pickthorn, K</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Winterton, Rt. Hon. Earl</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hutchinson, Geoffrey (Ilford, N.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pitman, I. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wood, Hon. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hutchison, Col. J. R. H. (Scotstoun)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Powell, J. Enoch</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>York, C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hut